    "statementHTML": "<div class=\"statement-body\">\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-goal\">\n   <h2><span class=\"icon icon-goal\">&nbsp;</span><span>Goal </span></h2>\n   <span class=\"question-statement\">You are given two integers <var>a</var> and <var>b</var>, and an operator <var>op</var>. Write the expression and its evaluation in vertical format.<br>For example, <const>123 + 456</const> is like the following:<br><pre style=\"font-family: monospace\"><br> 123<br>+456<br>----<br> 579<br></pre><br>Specially, if the operator is <strong>bit operation</strong> such as <const>&amp;</const><const>|</const>and<const>^</const>, you need to output the number in <strong>binary</strong> format.</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-protocol\">\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-input\">1 line, an integer <var>a</var>, a character <var>op</var> and another integer <var>b</var>. Seperated by space.</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-output\">4 lines, <strong>the length of lines depends on the longest line. Align the numbers to the right but align the operator to the left.</strong></div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Constraints</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-constraints\">0 &lt;= <var>a</var><var>b</var> &lt;= 1e6<br><var>op</var> is one of <const>+-*&amp;|^</const><br>The expression does not evaluate to a negative value.</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Example</div>\n      <div class=\"statement-inout\">\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-in\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-in\">123 + 456</pre>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-out\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-out\"> 123\n+456\n----\n 579</pre>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n   </div>\n</div>"
